The custom presentatio implementation. It contains a polyline based on an array of points.
This sample has animating of the polyline through an AIS_Shape and the custom presentation.

Test scenario:
- click 'AIS_Shape'
- click 'top'
- click 'fit all'
- change 'lines now' to 7000
- click 'run'
- zoom(with right mouse click and move) the end of the polyline (right bottom angle)
- uncheck 'run'
- uncheck 'AIS_Shape'
- click 'viewerLines_linePresentation'
- click 'run'
result: quicker than AIS_Shape

Platform:
  Windows, x64, VStudio 2019, cmake 3.5.4
3rd-parties:
  occt: 7.6.0
  qt: 5.15.1